#: ../../../customisation/announcement.md:1
msgid "Adding an announcement banner"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/announcement.md:7
msgid ""
"Furo makes it fairly straightforward to add a site-wide announcement (AKA "
"top banner). The announcement is added to the top of all pages on the "
"website."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/announcement.md:9
msgid ""
"This is done by setting `announcement` key in [`html_theme_options`][sphinx-"
"html_theme_options] in your `conf.py` file. The value of this key is HTML, "
"which is included as-is into the page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/announcement.md:11
msgid ""
"html_theme_options = {\n"
"    \"announcement\": \"<em>Important</em> announcement!\",\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../customisation/announcement.md:17
msgid ""
"The background and foreground of the announcement element are customisable, "
"via the mechanisms described in {doc}`colors`."
msgstr ""
